column2: SELECT   s.specObjID, s.ra, s.dec, s.z, s.zErr, s.class, s.zWarning, s.snMedian, zp.z, zp.zErr   CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestSpecObjEq(#, #, #) AS near   JOIN SpecObjAll as s ON near.specObjID=s.specObjID  JOIN Photoz as zp ON zp.objID = s.bestObjID  WHERE  s.class = &&& AND   s.zWarning=#
